## Editorial Workflow — team coordination + decision points
## Chief editor forms writer team, compiles output, requests human approval.

### Commission an article
POST http://localhost:9000/editorial
Content-Type: application/json

{"topic": "How remote work is reshaping city planning and urban design"}

### Check status — look for pendingQuestion when awaiting approval
GET http://localhost:9000/editorial/{{id}}

### Approve publication
POST http://localhost:9000/editorial/{{id}}/approve

### Reject with feedback (editor will revise with team)
POST http://localhost:9000/editorial/{{id}}/reject
Content-Type: application/json

{"reason": "The article needs stronger conclusions and expert quotes"}
